## Widget Methods

Once a widget is created, you can use several methods. For more information, see [Widget Methods](/api/widget-api/widget-methods/).

## Example

```javascript
// index.js
var widget = new widgetWindow({
  id: "myWidget",
  width: 300,
  height: 150,
  backgroundColor: "rgba(30, 30, 40, 0.9)",
});
```

